{"tid":668430,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選香港十大黑人憎政客","createTime":"2018-05-17T15:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T14:05:09.000Z","uid":14914,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad2f1f0a204923eb9234085b51bb966149ee175","tid":668430,"uid":14914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"你地最憎邊10個政客？<br />\n<br />\n根據維基百科 政客(政治人物)：政治人物，是指以政治為職業，或積極投入政治活動或公共事務的人，無論其動機是私人利益、黨派利益或國家利益。在現代民主政體中，職業政治人物常通過組織或加入政黨、參與選舉，以爭取在政府中擔任職務；這些人在英文中稱為「politician」，指的是一種社會角色。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先拋磚(頭盔：以下名稱不代表或影射任何人)：<br />\n689<br />\n777<br />\n垃圾筒局長<br />\n立會大口九<br />\n掃把頭<br />\n鼠王<br />\n元秋<br />\n鐵路主席<br />\n殺無赦"},{"pid":"e18d8a8187ee86babbe3b9226b904198682c57f1","tid":668430,"uid":63588,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"梁振英我屌你老母呀 使撚戴頭盔咩垃圾樓主"},{"pid":"22141de68a93535c1de7ee976ac4919a62e10dc7","tid":668430,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"要分開立法會議員同政府官各十人會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa01cd0257a5b480713c0d73c8a6f0c6201d1cd","tid":668430,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:02:56.000Z","msg":"揀十大唔黑人憎應該高難度好多"},{"pid":"b02f45bcc449d2c8467bf1377d5fd4022d377cba","tid":668430,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔係力架，係乞人"},{"pid":"704ac8061f76fb4aa50010d8890dcd9ccdc8dc51","tid":668430,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"邊個大口九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7379430ef1aac446369ec4324a4d0f41cc7ea897","tid":668430,"uid":126165,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"1.汪洋達<br />\n2.陳雲<br />\n3.鄭蟲太"},{"pid":"178a1e12ae42ea03ad323aa1bb40b2e6173f53b3","tid":668430,"uid":52221,"like